divs: sighting detailsmy friends and i were driving around my development when something caught my eye in the sky. the sky was overcast and the sun had just set. there were 3 lights stretching about 2\5 of the way down from the clouds but still 3\5 of the way above the ground. the lights illuminated the clouds where it penetrated and the light beams had a slighty larger diameter towards the bottom of the light compared to the top. the light created a cylinder like beam with almost a root like tip at the end. it was whitish and appeared slightly faded but still very noticable(lacked intensity). i have no idea what it was. no sound, movement, change in light intensity, theyre just there, my friends dropped me off at my house and i have no idea if the lights are still out there or not. side note my dog and neighborhood dogs were strangely acting up tonight.
